{"tid":2430760,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"張敬軒應該唔會再唱...","createTime":"2021-03-03T07:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T13:49:22.000Z","uid":206416,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a91e9348d4b25b305789e7336afbfe11383a6c1","tid":2430760,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"酩酊天使<br />\n<br />\n除咗佢講過因為呢首歌係講一位已經離世嘅好友。佢曾說過，呢首歌連哼一哼都會流淚，所以唔會再於live 演繹呢首歌。<br />\n<br />\n昨日Gary Tong 家中心臟病發離開咗，而呢首歌剛好係Gary Tong 親自編曲，所以更加幾乎肯定呢首歌係張敬軒歌單中永遠取消。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8733db4c42900f50173203145819cdec5643c0a1","tid":2430760,"uid":211578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"首歌真係聽到都好心噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810c9af4220ccfb7141e49dca96bf6266789e7a4","tid":2430760,"uid":206416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8733db4c42900f50173203145819cdec5643c0a1","tid":2430760,"uid":211578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"首歌真係聽到都好心噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />來生唔知有冇機會再聽到"},{"pid":"f9c25ea64dfded76bd347d0ddd4bd98aecef311b","tid":2430760,"uid":165341,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T07:14:27.000Z","msg":"好中意呢首歌<br />\n幾年前有個好親嘅人離開咗<br />\n機緣巧合之下認識到呢首歌<br />\n每次聽到嗰陣都好想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60274fc3b2735c819b9b98c8547c833ba4948937","tid":2430760,"uid":68689,"like":5